 method instead."}]}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"direction"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"direction","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"direction","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)direction","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1081","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"role":"symbol"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"topic","title":"MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/direction":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The heading of the map, measured in degrees clockwise from true north."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/direction","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"direction"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/direction","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"direction"}}}